# Task 6: Sales Trend Analysis Using Aggregations

## Objective
Analyze monthly revenue and order volume using SQL (SQLite).

## Steps Performed
- Created `online_sales` table
- Inserted sample data
- Used `strftime()` to extract year and month
- Grouped by year/month
- Aggregated using `SUM()` and `COUNT(DISTINCT order_id)`
- Ordered results chronologically

## Output
| Year | Month | Revenue | Orders |
|------|--------|---------|--------|
| 2023 | 01     | 350.00  | 2      |
| 2023 | 02     | 400.00  | 2      |
| 2023 | 03     | 170.00  | 1      |

## Tools Used
- SQLite v3.49.1 (Command Line)
